data.description: This gorgeously updated 5 bed/2 bath property has had the same owners for 3 decades and the care put into the home is evident. Featuring 3 bedrooms on the same level, hardwood floors on the upper level, brand new paint throughout in the last year, custom-built kitchen pantry and new whisper-close cabinets, new lighting, and stunning landscaping in the yard with perennials like Hydrangeas, Peonies, and Hostas, as well as 2 raised planters. New roof in 2022. Please see MLS supplements for a list of updates and don't forget to take the 3D virtual tour!
